@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ixehrw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.63 * ((v0 + 0.18 + v0 + 0.07) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.31)))
    tmp = ((0.60 * v2) / ((v0 + 0.44 * tmp + 0.98) - (v0 + 0.86 * v1 + 0.51)))
    v2 = (0.92 - 0.63)
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.32 - v2 + 0.19)) * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.86) / v1))
    v2 = 0.63
    data[tid] = v0
